<appendix id="checkouts"><title>Checkout commands</title>

<para>
First said, translators don't need to checkout the repository by
hand to translate the po files. They can get all files here:
</para>

<informalexample>
<screen>
&url-status;/&lt;LEVEL&gt;/files/&lt;LANGUAGECODE&gt;/
</screen>
</informalexample>

<para>
where &lt;LEVEL&gt; is either level1, level2, level3, level4 or
level5, and &lt;LANGUAGECODE&gt; is your language code like de, es, zh_CN, ...
</para>

<para>
POT templates can be found at:
</para>

<informalexample>
<screen>
&url-status;/&lt;LEVEL&gt;/POT/
</screen>
</informalexample>

