<sect3>
<title>Checkout commands for developers</title>

<para>
Developers need the following commands to checkout the whole source tree:
</para>

<informalexample>
  <screen>
git clone git@salsa.debian.org:installer-team/d-i.git
cd d-i
./scripts/git-setup
mr checkout
  </screen>
</informalexample>
